{"pid":"b2ce79f1f11607e414b64a8190921c25f19dee35","tid":1368002,"uid":55851,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1828d73a3a5c546823d18d27767fb6b95c879560","tid":1368002,"uid":152222,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"姐係聽日入元朗遊行唔會犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"遊行係犯法，但係表達訴求係唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"去元朗遊又得,去元朗行又得,得左<br />\n係遊行唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"冇錯喇，而家宗仔教埋我地點玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之聽日冇人遊行，大家用各種方式自己各自表達訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ad509cbbf2724abbc37fb46092f5d2090ff73a","tid":1368002,"uid":216789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:47:23.000Z","msg":"鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"56a3d88052e26d2cae3c1c3137f0f73cc03cbe2a","tid":1368002,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1828d73a3a5c546823d18d27767fb6b95c879560","tid":1368002,"uid":152222,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"姐係聽日入元朗遊行唔會犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"去悼念總理李鵬啊<br />\n犯咩法呀"},{"pid":"ccd4158fbb4090f8bf51c01a6667ea4ea60bb05c","tid":1368002,"uid":47647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"我聽日去追星呀屌你個閪！"},{"pid":"986842449e0d79625fc650a9ddaa8bf7ccdc7d7e","tid":1368002,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccd4158fbb4090f8bf51c01a6667ea4ea60bb05c","tid":1368002,"uid":47647,"lik